# System context

This repo is a **coach-first basketball practice planner** (V1).

Before coding, read and follow:

- [SYSTEM_PROMPT.md](../../SYSTEM_PROMPT.md) — UI contract, architecture, deploy workflow, constraints
- [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) — agent entry point and file map
- [SYSTEM_STRUCTURE.md](../../SYSTEM_STRUCTURE.md) — domain scope

**Non-negotiables:**

- Single home input: "What are you working on today?" (no second question field).
- Chips + grouped presets + collapsed "More" advanced tags — all multi-select; data in `app/lib/locale/uiCatalog.ts`.
- Minimal dark UI — no gradients/animations unless requested.
- **Auto-deploy:** after every code change, run `npm run deploy` (push to `main` → Vercel). Skip only if user says no push/commit.

Do not redesign the whole app or expand to V2 team/roster features unless the user asks.
